---
// Meta Banner - Explains this site is a RootSpec demo
---

<section data-test="meta-banner" class="meta-banner">
  <div class="meta-container">
    <p class="meta-text">
      This marketing site was <strong>generated from a ~100-line product description</strong>
      through the <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec" data-test="view-spec-link" class="spec-link">RootSpec pipeline</a>.
      View the <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/demos/blob/main/greenfield/SEED.md" class="seed-link">seed file</a>
      and <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/demos/tree/main/greenfield/rootspec" class="spec-link">complete specification</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.meta-banner {
  background: var(--color-surface-elevated);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  padding: var(--space-12) 0;
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
}

.meta-container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--space-16);
  text-align: center;
}

.meta-text {
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.spec-link,
.seed-link {
  color: var(--color-primary);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 500;
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: border-color 200ms ease;
}

.spec-link:hover,
.seed-link:hover {
  border-bottom-color: var(--color-primary);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .meta-banner {
    padding: var(--space-8) 0;
  }

  .meta-text {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
  }
}
</style>